name: Scrobblr App Redesign
description:
2nd Year College Project - UI Design


Briefed to create/redesign a soft prototype of a user interface (that may or may not already exist). This involved user journey and user testing, wireframing, rebranding and making a Figma prototype as the finished product. We also had to create a Behance project to as one of the deliverables.
